whom everyone can agree on.

551
00:43:16,860 --> 00:43:18,180
I'm baffled.

552
00:43:19,450 --> 00:43:21,520
I thought Lee Yeon-seo would be the one

553
00:43:22,620 --> 00:43:24,650
to bail out, not you people.

554
00:43:25,350 --> 00:43:28,250
Are you saying that she's going to quit?

555
00:43:28,340 --> 00:43:29,270
No.

556
00:43:29,350 --> 00:43:32,480
I'm talking about performing with you all.

557
00:43:33,400 --> 00:43:34,370
I was worried she'd say

558
00:43:34,460 --> 00:43:37,140
that she wouldn't be able to perform

559
00:43:37,670 --> 00:43:39,250
with such an incompetent corps.

560
00:43:40,090 --> 00:43:41,630
The five who performed "Spanish".

561
00:43:42,250 --> 00:43:44,490
Did you know the angles of your elbows
were terrible?

562
00:43:44,620 --> 00:43:45,720
Yi-geon.

563
00:43:45,810 --> 00:43:48,050
I said not to smile or frown excessively.

564
00:43:48,140 --> 00:43:50,610
But you had a stiff face all night long.
Were you at a funeral?

565
00:43:50,690 --> 00:43:51,750
Geum Ni-na!

566
00:43:52,370 --> 00:43:53,990
You were too focused on keeping the rhythm

567
00:43:54,080 --> 00:43:56,550
that your dance moves were dull,
yet you mentioned acknowledging

568
00:43:57,070 --> 00:43:58,040
and agreeing?

569
00:44:02,440 --> 00:44:03,760
I couldn't feel anything.

570
00:44:03,850 --> 00:44:05,170
Do you even listen to the music?

571
00:44:05,260 --> 00:44:06,800
Do you even understand the story?

572
00:44:06,890 --> 00:44:08,870
With Yeon-seo, she could just stand
in front of me,

573
00:44:08,950 --> 00:44:12,120
and my body would feel electrified.

574
00:44:12,210 --> 00:44:13,220
So how?

575
00:44:14,230 --> 00:44:16,560
How are all your dance moves

576
00:44:17,400 --> 00:44:19,160
so empty? How?

577
00:44:19,690 --> 00:44:20,740
Why?

578
00:44:31,740 --> 00:44:34,160
(With Yeon-seo, she could just stand
in front of me,)

579
00:44:34,250 --> 00:44:37,290
(and my body would feel electrified.)

580
00:44:37,380 --> 00:44:38,430
(So how?)

581
00:44:39,620 --> 00:44:43,270
(How are all your dance moves so empty?)

582
00:44:43,980 --> 00:44:45,030
(Why?)

583
00:44:52,690 --> 00:44:53,920
This is awful.

584
00:44:55,720 --> 00:44:58,010
I'm being awful to myself.

585
00:44:58,320 --> 00:45:01,490
It's so awful that I'm not Yeon-seo!

586
00:45:01,580 --> 00:45:03,950
What's there to yell about?

587
00:45:05,580 --> 00:45:07,250
You're totally wasted in broad daylight.

588
00:45:16,360 --> 00:45:17,370
Is that her?

589
00:45:18,430 --> 00:45:19,790
Ms. Elena?

590
00:45:20,100 --> 00:45:21,770
Ms. Elena!

591
00:45:22,870 --> 00:45:24,410
Ms. Elena!

592
00:45:28,370 --> 00:45:29,520
Ms. Elena!

593
00:45:30,700 --> 00:45:31,760
Ms. Elena.

594
00:45:32,290 --> 00:45:33,520
Ms. Elena.

595
00:45:34,000 --> 00:45:35,190
Ms. Elena.

596
00:45:36,120 --> 00:45:37,350
Ms. Elena!

597
00:45:39,200 --> 00:45:41,000
Is that you, Ms. Elena?

598
00:45:41,660 --> 00:45:43,330
It's me, Ni-na.

599
00:45:43,420 --> 00:45:47,120
I learned ballet from you when I was a kid
for the first time. I'm Geum Ni-na!

600
00:45:48,260 --> 00:45:49,540
Get lost!

601
00:45:49,620 --> 00:45:50,590
I...

602
00:45:50,900 --> 00:45:52,920
I thought about you from time to time.

603
00:45:53,800 --> 00:45:55,210
I missed you.

604
00:45:55,650 --> 00:45:57,460
I told you to get lost.

605
00:45:57,590 --> 00:46:00,230
The mere mention of Fantasia disgusts me.

606
00:46:00,310 --> 00:46:01,720
It makes my blood boil!

607
00:46:01,810 --> 00:46:02,910
Go away!

608
00:46:04,850 --> 00:46:06,390
I must be having a terrible day today.

609
00:46:22,930 --> 00:46:25,790
A list of guests and agencies
that participated in yesterday's event?

610
00:46:26,540 --> 00:46:28,870
Yes, there's something
I want to look into.

611
00:46:30,410 --> 00:46:31,550
Please.

612
00:46:33,710 --> 00:46:34,850
That's too bad.

613
00:46:35,210 --> 00:46:37,980
I can't share personal information
like that.

614
00:46:38,640 --> 00:46:39,650
Then

615
00:46:41,060 --> 00:46:43,350
why don't we investigate it together?

616
00:46:45,060 --> 00:46:46,780
Investigate what?

617
00:46:46,870 --> 00:46:48,540
Do you think that someone

618
00:46:49,150 --> 00:46:51,090
could have harmed Yeon-seo yesterday?

619
00:46:51,180 --> 00:46:52,810
I would like to believe that I'm wrong.

620
00:46:53,290 --> 00:46:54,300
That's why

621
00:46:55,490 --> 00:46:56,770
I want to look into this.

622
00:46:57,950 --> 00:47:00,070
Yeon-seo recently got her surgery.

623
00:47:00,150 --> 00:47:01,740
And she worked too much to return.

624
00:47:01,830 --> 00:47:03,010
Considering her circumstances,

625
00:47:03,100 --> 00:47:05,350
a glass of wine is enough to push her
over the edge.

626
00:47:05,430 --> 00:47:06,670
So you've already

627
00:47:06,750 --> 00:47:09,090
made up your mind that it is completely

628
00:47:09,530 --> 00:47:10,800
Yeon-seo's fault.

629
00:47:12,170 --> 00:47:14,010
There's no reason to deny that.

630
00:47:14,100 --> 00:47:15,290
Logically speaking.

631
00:47:17,580 --> 00:47:18,900
I understand.

632
00:47:21,540 --> 00:47:22,510
Actually, I expected

633
00:47:22,590 --> 00:47:25,320
that you would be eager
to help me investigate

634
00:47:26,290 --> 00:47:27,480
because you're her family.

635
00:48:28,060 --> 00:48:29,210
(Artistic Director's Office)

636
00:48:32,950 --> 00:48:34,400
What brings you here?

637
00:48:34,710 --> 00:48:36,200
Director Ji isn't here now.

638
00:48:38,360 --> 00:48:39,330
Excuse me.

639
00:48:40,380 --> 00:48:41,700
What do you think you're doing?

640
00:48:42,500 --> 00:48:44,340
Before I report you
for obstruction of business,

641
00:48:44,430 --> 00:48:45,660
leave immediately.

642
00:48:54,290 --> 00:48:55,610
I'll take care of him.

643
00:48:55,700 --> 00:48:56,930
Just keep an eye on him for now.

644
00:48:58,690 --> 00:48:59,740
He's cute.

645
00:49:06,040 --> 00:49:08,850
If I run the blood test now, I'll get
the result tonight at the earliest.

646
00:49:09,030 --> 00:49:10,130
Please take care of it.

647
00:49:11,010 --> 00:49:11,930
And you too.

648
00:49:12,020 --> 00:49:12,940
Don't you worry.

649
00:49:13,030 --> 00:49:15,850
I know a glass of wine won't
get you that drunk.

650
00:49:16,110 --> 00:49:17,120
Once we get the result,

651
00:49:17,210 --> 00:49:18,880
we might be able to catch who it is.

652
00:49:40,660 --> 00:49:42,470
I went to the ballet theatre.

653
00:49:44,750 --> 00:49:45,770
How is it there?

654
00:49:47,480 --> 00:49:48,760
Actually, it's so obvious.

655
00:49:48,850 --> 00:49:50,610
The sponsors probably demanded
to kick me out.

656
00:49:50,690 --> 00:49:52,230
And dancers will be gossiping about me.

657
00:49:52,320 --> 00:49:54,740
"She's unbelievable." "She was crazy."

658
00:49:58,310 --> 00:49:59,670
Everything will get resolved.

659
00:49:59,760 --> 00:50:01,690
I believe that it wasn't your fault.

660
00:50:01,780 --> 00:50:03,540
How will belief resolve anything?

661
00:50:26,550 --> 00:50:28,840
My gosh, you look gaunt.

662
00:50:29,410 --> 00:50:31,750
Why are you here?
What do you want to know?

663
00:50:31,830 --> 00:50:33,070
Don't be so cold.

664
00:50:33,150 --> 00:50:35,130
I barely managed to calm down
those sponsors

665
00:50:35,220 --> 00:50:37,250
who wanted to barge in here.

666
00:50:37,330 --> 00:50:38,570
What do they want?

667
00:50:38,650 --> 00:50:39,970
Do they want me to kneel down?

668
00:50:40,060 --> 00:50:42,040
It would be great if it was that simple.

669
00:50:53,920 --> 00:50:54,930
Mr. Park.

670
00:51:00,390 --> 00:51:02,940
(Withdrawal Agreement
on the Power of Attorney)

671
00:51:03,030 --> 00:51:04,960
I truly did my best to help you.

672
00:51:05,230 --> 00:51:06,500
When you weren't at your best,

673
00:51:06,590 --> 00:51:07,560
I tried to protect you

674
00:51:07,650 --> 00:51:09,140
by extending the power of attorney.

675
00:51:09,230 --> 00:51:11,120
And when you stubbornly asked me
to give it back,

676
00:51:11,210 --> 00:51:13,190
I even announced that
I would be resigning.

677
00:51:15,390 --> 00:51:16,360
You know what?

678
00:51:20,100 --> 00:51:21,900
Power of attorney or extension.

679
00:51:21,990 --> 00:51:23,400
Forget about those.

680
00:51:27,140 --> 00:51:28,330
Give everything to me.

681
00:51:29,030 --> 00:51:30,040
You must.

682
00:51:32,020 --> 00:51:34,440
I don't need money from
those perverted sponsors.

683
00:51:34,530 --> 00:51:36,640
I'll sell the house to pay for the show
if I need to.

684
00:51:36,730 --> 00:51:37,830
That's enough, right?

685
00:51:39,020 --> 00:51:40,870
It's not just about money.

686
00:51:40,960 --> 00:51:44,430
They even said that if we should send you
to a mental institution.

687
00:51:44,520 --> 00:51:47,510
They questioned how we could let a girl
who isn't in her right mind take over

688
00:51:47,600 --> 00:51:49,450
this big foundation
and the ballet theatre.

689
00:51:49,540 --> 00:51:50,550
I made

690
00:51:52,350 --> 00:51:53,410
one mistake that day.

691
00:51:56,490 --> 00:51:58,780
Or it could be a trap that someone set up.

692
00:52:00,360 --> 00:52:01,770
There you go again.

693
00:52:01,990 --> 00:52:03,130
Who on earth

694
00:52:03,220 --> 00:52:04,800
would set up this meticulous trap

695
00:52:04,890 --> 00:52:07,400
and go through all that trouble
just to kick you out?

696
00:52:08,370 --> 00:52:09,340
Oh, right.

697
00:52:10,880 --> 00:52:12,680
The ballet theatre will go on a strike.

698
00:52:13,030 --> 00:52:15,450
They can't perform with a girl like you.

699
00:52:15,540 --> 00:52:16,640
You understand that, right?

700
00:52:16,860 --> 00:52:19,190
Don't live in your memories
like an old lady.

701
00:52:19,280 --> 00:52:21,080
You're not the same Yeon-seo.

702
00:52:21,170 --> 00:52:23,940
No one is welcoming you back.

703
00:52:24,560 --> 00:52:25,570
Do you get that?

704
00:52:25,660 --> 00:52:27,110
Excuse me, ma'am!

705
00:52:27,990 --> 00:52:29,660
Gosh, you startled me.

706
00:52:29,750 --> 00:52:32,740
Did you just yell at me?

707
00:52:32,830 --> 00:52:33,710
There is a saying.

708
00:52:33,800 --> 00:52:36,350
"Throw out every kind or shape of evil."

709
00:52:36,880 --> 00:52:38,550
"Greed gives birth to sin."

710
00:52:38,640 --> 00:52:40,970
"When it's full-grown,
it gives birth to death."

711
00:52:41,460 --> 00:52:43,170
Hey, Dan. What's the matter with you?

712
00:52:43,260 --> 00:52:44,450
What's going on here?

713
00:52:44,540 --> 00:52:46,080
Have both of you gone crazy?

714
00:52:46,160 --> 00:52:47,790
I understand that you may
get carried away.

715
00:52:47,880 --> 00:52:49,150
I know that temptation is strong,

716
00:52:49,240 --> 00:52:52,810
but you're the only family Yeon-seo has.

717
00:52:53,600 --> 00:52:56,630
Why don't you cherish her?
Why don't you love her?

718
00:52:57,250 --> 00:52:59,890
How could you treat her no better
than a stranger?

719
00:53:00,290 --> 00:53:02,790
Why do you hurt her like this? Why?

720
00:53:04,690 --> 00:53:07,330
You are surely blessed with
having a loyal secretary.

721
00:53:07,410 --> 00:53:09,000
Mr. Jo and this guy now.

722
00:53:09,390 --> 00:53:11,680
They'll do everything for you.

723
00:53:11,950 --> 00:53:14,760
You must feel reassured
without your family.

724
00:53:18,150 --> 00:53:19,160
Leave now.

725
00:53:19,380 --> 00:53:20,790
Don't you ever come to see me.

726
00:53:26,160 --> 00:53:27,430
I'll give you 12 hours.

727
00:53:27,520 --> 00:53:28,580
Resign on your own.

728
00:53:28,670 --> 00:53:30,210
If you continue to be stubborn,

729
00:53:30,290 --> 00:53:32,270
all of the sponsors will leave.

730
00:53:32,360 --> 00:53:34,210
And once the reputation of Fantasia
is marred,

731
00:53:34,300 --> 00:53:36,670
this foundation your parents established

732
00:53:36,760 --> 00:53:39,090
will vanish into thin air.

733
00:53:40,060 --> 00:53:41,820
And the only person to stop that

734
00:53:41,910 --> 00:53:43,980
from happening is me, Choi Yeong-ja.

735
00:53:46,220 --> 00:53:47,190
Keep that in mind.

736
00:53:55,290 --> 00:53:56,780
Thank you for the juice.

737
00:54:18,210 --> 00:54:19,270
It's almost ready.

738
00:54:19,530 --> 00:54:22,390
Drink this and don't think about anything.
Just get some sleep.

739
00:54:31,540 --> 00:54:32,550
Let's go upstairs.

740
00:55:13,120 --> 00:55:14,220
What are you doing?

741
00:55:14,310 --> 00:55:15,630
No, stop drinking.

742
00:55:15,720 --> 00:55:16,990
Who do you think you are?

743
00:55:19,370 --> 00:55:20,470
Don't be such a fool.

744
00:55:20,560 --> 00:55:22,580
Why are you doing this
after what happened yesterday?

745
00:55:23,110 --> 00:55:24,470
You requested a blood test.

746
00:55:24,560 --> 00:55:25,620
When we get the result...

747
00:55:25,700 --> 00:55:26,850
It'll be useless.

748
00:55:29,220 --> 00:55:31,640
I'm sure someone put
a stimulant somewhere.

749
00:55:32,220 --> 00:55:33,360
But

750
00:55:33,580 --> 00:55:36,480
alcohol and sedatives were found
in your blood too.

751
00:55:36,570 --> 00:55:38,330
Did you take any medications?

752
00:55:40,840 --> 00:55:43,830
(Everything is mixed up, so they aren't
sure if it could be used as evidence.)

753
00:55:44,670 --> 00:55:46,470
They can't find out if what I had was

754
00:55:46,560 --> 00:55:48,580
poison, medication, or alcohol,

755
00:55:49,900 --> 00:55:51,800
or who did it to me.

756
00:55:53,780 --> 00:55:55,580
I must really have gone crazy.

757
00:55:55,670 --> 00:55:57,030
It's all my fault.

758
00:55:57,120 --> 00:55:58,660
I was going to keep my eyes open.

759
00:55:59,500 --> 00:56:00,990
I wanted to make sure I protect you.

760
00:56:03,100 --> 00:56:04,340
It's my fault.

761
00:56:04,690 --> 00:56:06,890
-No.
-You said

762
00:56:07,240 --> 00:56:08,910
greed gives birth to sin.

763
00:56:11,590 --> 00:56:13,350
I guess it was greed for me to wish

764
00:56:15,250 --> 00:56:16,480
to do ballet again.

765
00:56:21,410 --> 00:56:23,390
No. It isn't.

766
00:56:25,450 --> 00:56:27,130
My first audience said

767
00:56:27,480 --> 00:56:30,430
that my dance was the prettiest thing
he had ever seen in his life.

768
00:56:31,220 --> 00:56:33,150
A kid who didn't know what ballet is

769
00:56:34,430 --> 00:56:36,190
became touched and cried.

770
00:56:37,200 --> 00:56:38,350
(I know.)

771
00:56:39,230 --> 00:56:40,370
(I felt that way too.)

772
00:56:41,780 --> 00:56:44,730
I was so happy back then.

773
00:56:46,880 --> 00:56:49,080
He helped me realize

774
00:56:50,310 --> 00:56:51,810
that I'm happy when I dance.

775
00:56:54,670 --> 00:56:56,560
But I'd forgotten that
for such a long time.

776
00:56:57,880 --> 00:56:59,250
I finally

777
00:57:00,520 --> 00:57:02,280
found my goal again,

778
00:57:05,100 --> 00:57:06,200
but...

779
00:57:08,310 --> 00:57:09,410
it's too tough.

780
00:57:11,830 --> 00:57:12,970
It's tough.

781
00:57:39,330 --> 00:57:40,470
Young Lady.

782
00:57:43,640 --> 00:57:45,310
Can't you just give up on everything?

783
00:57:48,170 --> 00:57:49,930
I hate to see you suffer.

784
00:57:52,750 --> 00:57:54,730
You don't have to keep dancing

785
00:57:55,520 --> 00:57:57,020
for Fantasia.

786
00:57:59,700 --> 00:58:01,680
If you need an audience to dance,

787
00:58:03,310 --> 00:58:04,580
I will watch you.

788
00:58:06,430 --> 00:58:07,400
Okay?

789
00:58:10,880 --> 00:58:12,110
Should I?

790
00:58:13,960 --> 00:58:15,940
Should I give up on everything,

791
00:58:17,390 --> 00:58:19,410
show my dance only to you

792
00:58:20,780 --> 00:58:23,060
and live like that forever?

793
00:58:31,380 --> 00:58:32,480
Okay.

794
00:58:38,900 --> 00:58:41,460
I will give you my first performance.

795
00:58:43,480 --> 00:58:44,800
This piece is called

796
00:58:45,720 --> 00:58:46,820
"Giselle".

797
00:59:37,110 --> 00:59:38,300
It's you.

798
00:59:51,110 --> 00:59:52,250
Kim Dan.

799
00:59:54,140 --> 00:59:55,200
Yes, Young Lady.

800
00:59:57,970 --> 01:00:00,430
Why do you always save me?

801
01:00:04,260 --> 01:00:06,200
You save me

802
01:00:07,430 --> 01:00:09,150
and help me out.

803
01:00:09,980 --> 01:00:12,090
But why don't you like me?

804
01:00:15,750 --> 01:00:16,760
Figures.

805
01:00:17,330 --> 01:00:19,750
No one in this world likes me.

806
01:00:21,690 --> 01:00:23,400
I don't care about that.

807
01:00:25,290 --> 01:00:29,250
But it's not okay for you

808
01:00:31,760 --> 01:00:34,050
to not like me. I hate it.

809
01:00:34,890 --> 01:00:36,120
It's frustrating.

810
01:00:38,410 --> 01:00:40,080
You said I'm good.

811
01:00:41,570 --> 01:00:42,980
You said I'm pretty.

812
01:00:44,740 --> 01:00:45,750
But...

813
01:00:48,260 --> 01:00:50,330
But why don't you like me?

814
01:00:51,210 --> 01:00:52,930
How can you not like me?

815
01:00:55,700 --> 01:00:56,710
How?

816
01:00:58,160 --> 01:00:59,310
Kim Dan.

817
01:01:39,210 --> 01:01:40,270
I...

818
01:01:42,560 --> 01:01:44,140
cannot like you.

819
01:01:45,550 --> 01:01:46,650
And I...

820
01:01:49,900 --> 01:01:51,530
can't stay by your side forever.

821
01:01:52,720 --> 01:01:53,860
That really

822
01:01:54,880 --> 01:01:56,280
breaks my heart.

823
01:01:57,300 --> 01:01:58,350
Yeon-seo.

824
01:01:59,320 --> 01:02:00,460
How can I

825
01:02:04,160 --> 01:02:05,700
not like you?

826
01:02:21,140 --> 01:02:22,290
Don't go.

827
01:02:25,850 --> 01:02:27,040
Don't go.

828
01:02:29,500 --> 01:02:31,130
How do you really feel?

829
01:02:31,310 --> 01:02:33,820
Are you worried he isn't the real one?

830
01:02:33,900 --> 01:02:36,460
Or are you wishing
that he isn't the real one?

831
01:02:45,520 --> 01:02:47,100
I'm in huge trouble, aren't I?

832
01:02:51,550 --> 01:02:53,660
-What are you doing?
-No, what's with you?

833
01:02:55,420 --> 01:02:57,800
-Let go of me. Let go...
-You can't run away.

834
01:02:57,880 --> 01:03:00,570
Tell me you'll disappear
from Yeon-seo's life now.

835
01:03:00,650 --> 01:03:01,750
What are you talking about?

836
01:03:01,840 --> 01:03:03,030
I warned you, didn't I?

837
01:03:03,290 --> 01:03:04,970
That I won't let you live
if you interfere.

838
01:03:05,050 --> 01:03:06,770
Who do you think you are to tell her

839
01:03:06,860 --> 01:03:08,620
to give up on dancing?

840
01:03:10,550 --> 01:03:11,610
I said, let go!

841
01:04:01,680 --> 01:04:05,110
(Angel's Last Mission: Love)

842
01:04:06,650 --> 01:04:09,030
(You promised me that whatever you do,)

843
01:04:09,120 --> 01:04:10,660
you'll do it to make Yeon-seo happy.

844
01:04:10,830 --> 01:04:11,710
(What's with me?)

845
01:04:11,800 --> 01:04:13,030
He really gets on my nerves.

846
01:04:13,120 --> 01:04:14,180
Hey, what are you doing?

847
01:04:14,270 --> 01:04:15,810
(No matter what you choose to do,)

848
01:04:15,890 --> 01:04:17,430
you are no longer alone.

849
01:04:19,500 --> 01:04:21,090
(I'll make sure you like it.)

850
01:04:21,480 --> 01:04:23,290
I'll make you love it.

851
01:04:26,280 --> 01:04:28,740
(What are you doing to Yeon-seo?)

852
01:04:29,010 --> 01:04:32,170
Mr. Kim. No. Angel Dan.

853
01:04:32,350 --> 01:04:34,290
Why are you here?
